# ============================================================
#  Backlog Manager — API Keys
#
#  You do NOT need this file to run the app.
#  All API keys are managed inside the app via the
#  ⚙️ Settings screen in the sidebar.
#
#  Keys are encrypted and stored at:
#    %AppData%\Backlog Manager\api-keys.enc  (Windows)
#
#  The following keys are required for full functionality:
#
#  TMDB_API_KEY        — Movies & TV (themoviedb.org/settings/api)
#  IGDB_CLIENT_ID      — Games, from dev.twitch.tv/console
#  IGDB_ACCESS_TOKEN   — Games, generated via Twitch OAuth
#  GOOGLE_PLACES_KEY   — Restaurants, from console.cloud.google.com
#
#  AniList (Anime) requires no API key.
# ============================================================